trans-unit.source: Provides data related to the <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement.SizeChanged"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Gir data relatert til det <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement.SizeChanged"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height*> component of the size changed.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height*>komponent i størrelsen endres.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height*>

trans-unit.source: Because <xref:System.Double> precision numbers process imprecisely, this property might return a value of `false` even when <xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventArgs.PreviousSize%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventArgs.NewSize%2A> are not equal.
trans-unit.target: Fordi <xref:System.Double>presisjon tall prosessen imprecisely, denne egenskapen kan returnere en verdi for `false` selv når <xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventArgs.PreviousSize%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventArgs.NewSize%2A>er ikke identiske.</xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventArgs.NewSize%2A> </xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventArgs.PreviousSize%2A> </xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: The layout system occasionally experiences this state due to minor fluctuations in the input parameters; however, the overall rendered scene is considered to be the same; therefore, no visible changes are detected.
trans-unit.target: Oppsettet systemet oppstår noen ganger denne tilstanden på grunn av underordnede variasjoner i inndataparameterne; imidlertid anses generelle gjengitte scene å være den samme. Derfor finner ingen synlige endringer.

trans-unit.source: The handler for the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.SizeChanged> event should check for this state in order to avoid invalidation of layout if the dimension didn't actually change.
trans-unit.target: Et behandlingsprogram for den <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.SizeChanged>hendelsen skal se etter denne tilstanden for å unngå invalidation oppsett hvis dimensjonen faktisk ikke ble endret.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.SizeChanged>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height*> component of the size changed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height*>sekundkomponenten størrelsen endret; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height*>

trans-unit.source: Invokes event handlers in a type-specific way, which can increase event system efficiency.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer hendelsesbehandling på en måte typespesifikke, noe som kan øke hendelsen system effektivitet.

trans-unit.source: This implementation casts the generic handler as a <xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventHandler> and then invokes it.
trans-unit.target: Denne implementeringen kaster generisk behandlingsprogrammet som en <xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventHandler>og aktiverer det.</xref:System.Windows.SizeChangedEventHandler>

trans-unit.source: For details on this implementation pattern and the reasons for it, see <xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventArgs.InvokeEventHandler%2A> and [Routed Events Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer informasjon om denne implementeringen mønsteret og årsaker til den <xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventArgs.InvokeEventHandler%2A>og [rutet hendelser oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.RoutedEventArgs.InvokeEventHandler%2A>

trans-unit.source: The generic handler to call in a type-specific way.
trans-unit.target: Generell behandlingsprogrammet å kalle på en typespesifikke måte.

trans-unit.source: The target to call the handler on.
trans-unit.target: Målet å kalle behandlingsprogrammet på.
